Script to instal Singularita's fork of CKAN on CENTOS7.
After you run this script you need to edit file /var/lib/solr/ckan/conf/solrconfig.xml thusly:
replace 
<schemaFactory class="ManagedIndexSchemaFactory">
    <bool name="mutable">true</bool>
    <str name="managedSchemaResourceName">managed-schema</str>
</schemaFactory>

with
 <schemaFactory class="ClassicIndexSchemaFactory"/>
 </schemaFactory>
